<div class="content">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/20355486" target="_blank" data-id="322537" data-za-element-name="Title">
关于nodejs的模板引擎，如何选择 EJS 和 Jade？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/20355486/answer/14871289">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="1072082">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="14871289"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>125</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
