<div class="content">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/20821569" target="_blank" data-id="509149" data-za-element-name="Title">
CSS 中，position：absolute、float、display：inline-block 都能实现相同效果，区别是什么？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/20821569/answer/16303485">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="1651559">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="16303485"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>124</a>
</div>

