<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">

<span class="summary-wrapper">
<span class="author-link-line">

<a class="author-link"
data-hovercard="p$t$ysbl"
target="_blank" href="/people/ysbl"
>一丝</a><span class="icon icon-badge-best_answerer icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$优秀回答者"></span></span><span class="badge-summary"><a href="/people/ysbl#hilightbadge" target="_blank">CSS、前端开发话题优秀回答者</a></span>



<span title="CSS 下面专家（阿里巴巴前端开发）" class="bio">
CSS 下面专家（阿里巴…
</span>
</span>
