<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/33864532" target="_blank" data-id="5752478" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何理解 Facebook 的 flux 应用架构？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/33864532/answer/76482275">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="26017629">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="76482275"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>123</a>
