<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/25264225" target="_blank" data-id="2288252" data-za-element-name="Title">
做前端和做 Java 或 C++ 相比前途哪个更好？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/25264225/answer/30334458">
